<br>
&quot;It's okay, Kyonae.  You did your best.&quot;  Menion shot a glare at the void demon but it was more out of worry for the mage than anger towards Mirak.  Ice mages, and elves in general were very skilled in healing and they thought nothing of bringing someone back from the edge of death.  It came as second nature for them.  But it took so much power for them to use death magic, (more Naomi's field than Kyonae's) that it always left them drained and weak.  Elves were never meant to harm, only to heal.  Dark elves were an exception.<br>
<br>
Kyonae staggered back and leaned into his grasp, trying to balance herself and failed.  Menion just sighed and picked her up, holding her effortlessly because she weighed so little.  &quot;so what do we do now? I agree with Mirak...attacking the leader of these guys seems to be the best option.  But how are we going to find out who it is?&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;I have an idea,&quot; Naomi purred.  &quot;These soldiers are not of an independent faction.  They are from the Osiria Army.  See their badges?  Now King Jio certainly would not have the brains to send an attack, or the will, because he really cares nothing for us.&quot;  She shrugged.  &quot;It seems that maybe we should look for the commander of the army.  For years the King and the military have been at odds.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;I say we just blast them all,&quot; Ember stated.  &quot;Just one good fire spell and BAM!  It's all over.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;No, Ember,&quot; Menion shook his head.  &quot;We can't do that.  There are innocent lives at stake.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;No Osirian is innocent,&quot; Ember spat.<br>
<br>
&quot;Neither is any Dratilian,&quot; Naomi shot back calmly.  Ember shut up immediately, looking guilty.  &quot;We'll find the commander of the army.  No doubt he--or she--is in hiding now.  He would not dare to stay in one place.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#060C65><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bcollisionworld.showUserPublicProfile?gid=spark@collisionworld>Spark</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://www.cheatingdome.com/forums/attachment.php?s=&postid=65686" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Member</span><br>  Posts: 99<br> <font color=#F5F5DC>(3/4/03 7:12 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fcollisionworldfrm147.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=6.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Search</span><hr size=1> **continued from &quot;Pheonix in his castle&quot; in &quot;castles&quot;<br>
