<br>
Cedric looked at Menion meaningfully, silencing him and at the same time telling him silently that it was the matter of stronger mages and beings than himself.  &quot;Mirak is right.  During the Siren Wars, Void Demons were present about Mahtim, drawn by the evil. It is still there, in the Unknown Regions, shrouded by forest(OOC: You mean the Restng in Unknown Regions topic??? *slightly confused*).&quot;<br>
