Mirak looked at Kyonae and stepped over to her looking at her with all three eyes. &quot;The portal is created by Void Magic, which feeds of pure evil so it would most surely kill her in this state. I have a idea but I have not tried something like this in many years&quot; Mirak said and started casting a spell on Kyonae.<br>
